ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Wonderful course, with a great mix of mainstream and not-so-mainstream authors. Does a great job tracing the course of critical history, starting with the New Critics and moving through reader-response criticism and New Historicism. Caleb is a very open and available professor, with much to teach -- a great ally and supporter.
